<div class="container">
    <h1>Make a Difference: Justice for All</h1>
    <p>Our justice system has loopholes that affect the lives of many. Together, we can bring change!</p>

    <div class="issue">
        <strong>1. Long Delays in Cases:</strong>
        <p>Many cases take years to resolve, causing frustration and suffering.</p>
        <div class="fix">
            <strong>Solution:</strong> We need more judges and efficient systems to speed up the process.
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="issue">
        <strong>2. Corruption:</strong>
        <p>Corruption can affect fair judgments and access to justice.</p>
        <div class="fix">
            <strong>Solution:</strong> Promote transparency and hold corrupt officials accountable.
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="issue">
        <strong>3. Lack of Legal Aid:</strong>
        <p>Many people cannot afford legal help, leaving them vulnerable.</p>
        <div class="fix">
            <strong>Solution:</strong> Strengthen legal aid services to ensure everyone has access to justice.
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="issue">
        <strong>4. Overlapping Laws:</strong>
        <p>Confusing laws can lead to misuse and injustice.</p>
        <div class="fix">
            <strong>Solution:</strong> Regularly review and clarify laws for better understanding.
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="issue">
        <strong>5. Victim Rights:</strong>
        <p>Victims often lack support in the legal process.</p>
        <div class="fix">
            <strong>Solution:</strong> Establish services to support and inform victims during cases.
        </div>
    </div>

    <button onclick="alert('Thank you for your interest! Join us in advocating for justice reform!')">Join the Movement!</button>
